name: TotemZ - The Silver Horse
description: TotemZ animal spirit #4 - The Horse ! What distinguishes the horse from other animals is its ability to face the obstacles of life. Fiery, impetuous and full of vitality, he represents the driving force of life. Torn between his desire for liberty and his humble obedience to man. The horse represents the duality between obligations and desires. Find more info on https://www.totemz-gallery.com
